title: Gennaro's Sweet Pepper Frittata
description:
Food Tube favourite Gennaro is back sharing his recipe for a delicious sweet pepper frittata that's perfect served hot or cold.

Filmed on the beautiful island of Malta this colourful and tasty dish is so easy to make and ideal for packed lunches or as a picnic treat.

So what do you put in your frittata Food Tubers? Please share any great recipes in the comments box below.
